"We‚Äôll start with the validation of the provided environment variables. "
"You can throw an error if required environment variables haven‚Äôt been "
"provided or if they don‚Äôt meet your predefined requirements. For this "
"purpose, we are going to use the npm package `Joi "
"<https://github.com/hapijs/joi>`__. With Joi, you define an object schema"
" and validate JavaScript objects against it."
msgstr ""

